name: FinanceApp
description:
24B is a personal bank UI kit that was specifically designed for iOS devices. It includes 52 carefully crafted mobile application screens that you can use to make your next iOS mobile application project brighter and more appealing to potential users.


This UI kit is FREE to download and use for both personal and commercial use and it's available for Adobe XD and Sketch as well. We have also created dark screens for popular "Dark Mode" that is also easy to customize.


Icons and font are free to use. Font used is Montserrat and can be download for free on www.fonts.google.com


If you have any questions or requests, please feel free to leave them all in the comments section below or reach out at support@broworks.net


Enjoy!

Broworks Team
